<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" name="viewport">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
  <title>Welcome to the Workers Make Possible Blog | Workers Make Possible</title>
  <style>
    /* ── Shared responsive helpers ── */
    .mobile-display  { display: none  }
    .desktop-display { display: block }
    @media (max-width: 1206px) {
      .desktop-display { display: none  }
      .mobile-display  { display: block }
    }

    /* ── Brand colours ── */
    :root {
      --yellow: #FDD24F;
      --red:    #C9112B;
      --navy:   #37375E;
    }

    /* ── Desktop nav ── */
    .titlebanner  { background-color: var(--yellow); height: 60px; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; z-index: 999; }
    .title        { position: fixed; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); font-weight: bold; z-index: 999; color: var(--red); }
    .logo         { position: fixed; z-index: 1000; height: 130px; width: 130px; background-color: transparent; top: -5px; }
    .deskybutton  { width: 100%; }
    .moveleft     { margin-left: 130px; }
    .navbanner    { background-color: white; height: 50px; position: fixed; top: 60px; z-index: 999; }
    .navcol       { position: relative; left: 150px; margin-right: 30px; top: 5px; }
    .navbutton    { background-color: transparent; border-radius: 20px; color: var(--navy); }
    .navbutton:hover { background-color: var(--yellow); font-weight: bold; }
    .currentpage  { background-color: var(--yellow); font-weight: bold; }
    .start        { position: relative; top: 130px; padding-bottom: 60px; }
    a             { color: var(--navy); }
    a:hover       { color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; }
    .h3           { color: var(--red); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════ DESKTOP ═══════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="desktop-display">
    <div class="titlebanner container-fluid"></div>
    <div class="title container h1"><span class="moveleft">Workers Make Possible</span></div>
    <div class="container h1">
      <button class="logo btn btn-lg btn-block">
        <img src="https://github.com/workersmakepossible/labourday/blob/main/assets/wmp_logo.png?raw=true"
             class="deskybutton img-responsive">
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="navbanner container-fluid">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="navcol"><button class="btn navbutton"><a href="https://workersmakepossible.com">Home</a></button></div>
          <div class="navcol"><button class="btn navbutton"><a href="https://workersmakepossible.com/labourday">Labour Day</a></button></div>
          <div class="navcol"><button class="btn navbutton"><a href="https://endlorryrides.com">End Lorry Rides</a></button></div>
          <div class="navcol"><button class="btn navbutton"><a href="https://workersmakepossible.substack.com/">Commentary</a></button></div>
          <div class="navcol"><button class="btn navbutton currentpage"><a href="/blog/">Blog</a></button></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="start">
      <div class="container">
        <style>
  .post-title   { color: #C9112B; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .post-meta    { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .post-content { color: #37375E; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .post-content h2, .post-content h3 { color: #C9112B; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  .post-content img { max-width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; margin: 16px 0; }
  .post-content a { color: #C9112B; }
  .post-content blockquote {
    border-left: 4px solid #FDD24F;
    padding-left: 16px;
    color: #555;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .back-link { 
    display: inline-block; 
    margin-bottom: 20px; 
    color: #37375E; 
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: #C9112B; text-decoration: none; }
  hr.post-divider { border-color: #C9112B; }
</style>

<a class="back-link" href="/blog/">&larr; Back to Blog</a>

<h1 class="post-title">Welcome to the Workers Make Possible Blog</h1>
<p class="post-meta">
  March 18, 2026
  &middot; Workers Make Possible
  &middot; 
    <span class="badge badge-warning">announcement</span> <span class="badge badge-warning">workers-rights</span> 
  
</p>
<hr class="post-divider">

<div class="post-content">
  <p>Welcome to our new blog! This is where we’ll share in-depth analysis, workers’ stories, and updates from our campaigns.</p>

<h2 id="why-a-blog">Why a Blog?</h2>

<p>While our <a href="https://workersmakepossible.substack.com/">Substack commentary</a> covers major pieces, this blog lets us share quicker updates, event recaps, and resources for workers.</p>

<h2 id="what-to-expect">What to Expect</h2>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Campaign updates</strong> — progress on our key demands</li>
  <li><strong>Worker stories</strong> — first-hand accounts from workers</li>
  <li><strong>Resources</strong> — guides and tools to support workers facing issues</li>
  <li><strong>Event coverage</strong> — recaps from actions and events</li>
</ul>

<p>Stay tuned, and thank you for your solidarity. ✊</p>

</div>

